26:42.600 --> 26:44.980
♪ I mean baby I miss you ♪

26:45.000 --> 26:47.270
♪ I mean baby I love you ♪

26:47.340 --> 26:49.550
♪ My heart rate's been racing
for so long ♪

26:49.590 --> 26:51.590
♪ Doctor, should you give me first aid? ♪

26:51.610 --> 26:53.120
♪ Waiting for you ♪

27:10.400 --> 27:11.400
Bravo!

27:16.950 --> 27:17.750
Mu.

27:18.510 --> 27:20.080
You're so cool playing the drums.

27:20.080 --> 27:21.190
It's nothing.

27:21.360 --> 27:22.880
Come on, show us your trump card.

27:22.880 --> 27:24.330
Sing a classic song

27:24.360 --> 27:25.560
and blow their minds.

27:27.760 --> 27:30.080
But Jin Zhao hasn't arrived yet.

27:30.430 --> 27:32.670
I want to sing this song for him.

27:33.320 --> 27:34.920
He's not here yet?

27:35.030 --> 27:36.120
That's weird.

27:36.310 --> 27:38.440
Sui talked to him today,

27:38.470 --> 27:40.620
and he asked about
our time and location tonight.

27:40.620 --> 27:42.050
I thought he was coming.

27:42.320 --> 27:44.450
Maybe he's still busy with something.

28:05.710 --> 28:07.040
Now you can sing, right?

28:09.120 --> 28:09.840
Come on.

28:12.900 --> 28:13.530
Next up,

28:13.560 --> 28:15.920
my good friend Jiang Mu

28:16.120 --> 28:18.080
will perform

28:18.270 --> 28:20.070
"The Moon Represents My Heart."

28:32.710 --> 28:38.730
♪ You ask me how deep I love you ♪

28:39.120 --> 28:43.710
♪ How much I love you ♪

28:44.580 --> 28:47.760
♪ My love is real ♪

28:47.790 --> 28:50.720
♪ My love is sincere ♪

28:50.880 --> 28:56.530
♪ The moon represents my heart ♪

28:57.640 --> 29:03.500
♪ You ask me how deep I love you ♪

29:03.800 --> 29:08.470
♪ How much I love you ♪

29:09.500 --> 29:12.710
♪ My love will never change ♪

29:12.740 --> 29:15.610
♪ My love will stay the same ♪

29:15.780 --> 29:20.960
♪ The moon represents my heart ♪

29:21.830 --> 29:27.380
♪ A gentle kiss ♪

29:28.080 --> 29:33.830
♪ Has touched my heart ♪

29:34.140 --> 29:40.030
♪ A deep love ♪

29:40.460 --> 29:46.640
♪ Has me miss you till now♪

29:47.270 --> 29:52.950
♪ You ask me how deep I love you ♪

29:53.080 --> 29:57.930
♪ How much I love you ♪

29:58.880 --> 30:02.030
♪ Go think about it ♪

30:02.080 --> 30:05.100
♪ Go take a look ♪

30:05.240 --> 30:10.950
♪ The moon represents my heart ♪

