♪ You ask me how deep I love you ♪

31:06.690 --> 31:11.650
♪ How much I love you ♪

31:12.570 --> 31:15.660
♪ Go think about it ♪

31:15.780 --> 31:18.610
♪ Go take a look ♪

31:18.800 --> 31:24.060
♪ The moon represents my heart ♪

31:24.840 --> 31:27.870
♪ Go think about it ♪

31:27.890 --> 31:30.970
♪ Go take a look ♪

31:31.000 --> 31:36.820
♪ The moon represents my heart ♪

32:23.670 --> 32:25.670
New Year's right around the corner.

32:28.800 --> 32:29.510
Is it?

32:30.360 --> 32:32.490
It's New Year's Eve in a couple of days.

32:33.510 --> 32:34.230
How did you

32:34.360 --> 32:36.420
usually spend New Year's Eve before?

32:39.430 --> 32:40.160
I forgot.

32:41.010 --> 32:42.810
It never crossed my mind before,

32:44.160 --> 32:45.560
so I never celebrated it.

32:47.270 --> 32:48.360
What about this year?

32:48.360 --> 32:49.820
How do you plan to spend it?

32:54.990 --> 32:55.850
What about you?

32:57.190 --> 32:58.390
Do you have any ideas?

33:00.570 --> 33:01.960
I heard from Sanlai

33:02.270 --> 33:05.260
that Manshi streets have a really
festive New Year atmosphere.

33:05.260 --> 33:07.630
There are temple fairs
and dragon and lion dances.

33:07.630 --> 33:08.690
Have you seen them?

33:09.080 --> 33:10.080
You want to go see?

33:18.800 --> 33:21.060
What kind of New Year gift would you like?

33:21.920 --> 33:22.780
What about you?

33:23.580 --> 33:25.240
What New Year gift do you want?

33:25.270 --> 33:27.200
If I tell you, will you give it to me?

33:30.470 --> 33:32.270
I can't get the moon from the sky,

33:32.890 --> 33:33.950
but anything else,

33:34.030 --> 33:35.690
I'll try my best to get for you.

33:38.080 --> 33:39.940
I don't want the moon from the sky.

33:40.230 --> 33:41.830
I'm already the moon myself.

34:10.250 --> 34:11.650
I'll go look at the waves.

34:20.800 --> 34:22.840
My New Year's wish is

34:23.110 --> 34:24.840
that the person in my heart

34:25.030 --> 34:26.550
can understand my songs,

34:26.949 --> 34:28.510
understand my feelings,

34:28.949 --> 34:30.550
and keep me in his heart

34:30.800 --> 34:32.670
as his moon for a lifetime!

34:32.989 --> 34:33.920
What did you say?

34:34.440 --> 34:37.070
The wind is too strong,
and I couldn't hear clearly.

34:37.070 --> 34:37.920
I was singing.

34:37.949 --> 34:39.030
Didn't you hear me?

34:41.489 --> 34:42.690
I'll sing again then!

35:21.800 --> 35:23.800
The sea at night is also beautiful.

35:36.680 --> 35:42.590
♪ You ask me how deep I love you ♪

35:43.070 --> 35:48.200
♪ How much I love you ♪

35:48.590 --> 35:51.760
♪ My love will never change ♪

35:52.110 --> 35:54.990
♪ My love will stay the same ♪

36:18.760 --> 36:19.800
It's getting late.

36:19.800 --> 36:20.930
We should head back.

36:22.430 --> 36:24.110
I heard there's a meteor shower tonight.

36:24.110 --> 36:25.360
Let's wait and see.

36:28.240 --> 36:29.510
Please.

36:35.840 --> 36:37.510
Remember last time
we watched the Orionids?

36:37.510 --> 36:39.240
You brought me here to see them.

36:39.720 --> 36:42.320
Back then, you couldn't
even tell directions.

36:43.110 --> 36:44.360
It's different now.

36:44.510 --> 36:46.550
I've fallen in love with astronomy.

36:46.800 --> 36:48.520
Those meteor showers

36:48.550 --> 36:50.150
are a piece of cake for me now.

36:51.140 --> 36:52.000
Have you heard?

36:52.130 --> 36:53.280
If you make wishes to meteor showers,

36:53.280 --> 36:55.140
they're more likely to come true.

36:59.200 --> 37:00.240
What's your wish?

37:01.550 --> 37:02.880
Never thought about it.

37:08.400 --> 37:09.860
You must have many wishes.

37:11.840 --> 37:12.760
How do you know?

37:13.470 --> 37:14.510
What's your wish?

37:16.630 --> 37:17.360
Guess.

37:32.280 --> 37:35.510
♪ Night is painted with neon lights ♪

37:35.710 --> 37:38.790
♪ The street is gentle and busy ♪

37:39.020 --> 37:42.860
♪ I paused and wandered far ♪

37:41.440 --> 37:43.210
Mu. Mu?

37:43.250 --> 37:46.900
♪ You're like a breeze ♪

37:47.690 --> 37:50.210
♪ I watch you leave ♪

37:51.020 --> 37:54.460
♪ I wish I could hug you from the back ♪

37:54.920 --> 37:57.990
♪ Lingering in the air ♪

37:58.300 --> 38:01.460
♪ Your breath is everywhere ♪

38:03.050 --> 38:06.200
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

38:03.880 --> 38:04.920
Zhao and Mu.

38:06.510 --> 38:09.450
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

38:07.240 --> 38:08.430
Never be apart.

38:09.920 --> 38:13.710
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

38:13.730 --> 38:18.420
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

38:18.530 --> 38:21.210
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

38:21.600 --> 38:25.050
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

38:25.610 --> 38:27.880
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

38:27.960 --> 38:31.640
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

38:31.660 --> 38:36.780
♪ This heart that wanders with you ♪

38:37.050 --> 38:40.640
♪ Only wishes you'd smile ♪

38:40.870 --> 38:44.850
♪ All the withered grass on earth ♪

38:44.970 --> 38:49.740
♪ Has bloomed for you ♪

38:55.920 --> 38:56.590
Mu.

38:59.280 --> 39:00.680
How do you know Zhang Fan?

39:02.760 --> 39:05.200
The guy who stood on your left yesterday.

39:05.400 --> 39:06.590
He's not a good person.

39:06.590 --> 39:08.950
He's a bad guy. Stay away from him.

39:09.990 --> 39:11.200
How's he a bad guy?

39:11.360 --> 39:13.240
He loafs around all day

39:13.400 --> 39:14.340
and never does anything serious.

39:14.340 --> 39:15.960
You can tell at a glance
he won't get into college.

39:15.960 --> 39:17.840
He's been in this foundation course
for 3 years—

39:17.840 --> 39:19.640
he's basically a street guy now.

39:25.760 --> 39:26.820
Where's the money?

39:31.680 --> 39:33.810
If you're late with it again next time,

39:34.000 --> 39:34.840
you're dead.

39:36.760 --> 39:37.630
You know him?

39:38.200 --> 39:38.950
Yes.

39:40.070 --> 39:40.600
Let's go.

39:40.650 --> 39:41.510
Take me to him.

39:41.590 --> 39:42.280
Mu!

39:43.360 --> 39:44.510
Hey, Mu, you really can't go!

39:44.510 --> 39:45.430
He's a street guy.

39:45.430 --> 39:47.830
Why would you want to
get involved with him?

39:49.800 --> 39:50.510
You go.

39:51.630 --> 39:52.420
Me?

40:02.070 --> 40:02.870
Leave it to me.

40:21.400 --> 40:23.400
Someone's looking for you outside.

40:26.150 --> 40:27.680
Can't you see I'm sleeping?

40:28.510 --> 40:29.200
Who is it?

40:43.950 --> 40:44.800
Oh, it's you.

40:45.200 --> 40:46.200
Do you know Jin...

40:47.590 --> 40:49.050
I mean, do you know Brandy?

40:50.680 --> 40:51.470
Yes, I do.

40:52.240 --> 40:52.990
What's up?

40:53.950 --> 40:54.920
Are you close?

40:56.200 --> 40:58.260
My brother is pretty close with Brandy.

40:58.260 --> 40:59.340
Your brother?

41:01.320 --> 41:02.450
Who's your brother?

41:02.510 --> 41:04.570
Why are you asking so many questions?

41:04.720 --> 41:06.920
What's your relationship with Brandy?

41:08.880 --> 41:09.840
I'm...

41:09.990 --> 41:11.990
I'm his tenant.

41:12.590 --> 41:13.320
Well...

41:14.720 --> 41:15.550
What was in that package

41:15.550 --> 41:17.550
you gave to Brandy yesterday?

41:17.930 --> 41:18.740
Blueprints.

41:19.990 --> 41:22.240
My brother asked me to give them
to Brandy.

41:22.240 --> 41:22.970
Blueprints?

41:24.400 --> 41:25.840
They were

41:26.200 --> 41:29.400
complete structural blueprints of a car.

41:31.470 --> 41:32.920
Blueprints?

41:33.150 --> 41:34.330
You... You...

41:34.360 --> 41:36.320
So who's your brother?

41:38.510 --> 41:39.910
An automotive engineer.

41:40.070 --> 41:41.470
He works at a car factory.

41:41.630 --> 41:42.840
Why are you asking so much?

41:42.840 --> 41:43.470
What,

41:43.840 --> 41:45.900
you want to get to know my brother too?

41:48.470 --> 41:49.240
I don't.

41:49.760 --> 41:50.510
Thanks.

41:51.460 --> 41:53.750
So many pointless questions.

41:55.240 --> 41:57.040
Hey, how can you be so shameless?

41:59.470 --> 42:01.360
Mu, are you okay? Did he scare you?

42:02.510 --> 42:03.840
Do you know Seventh Day?

42:04.320 --> 42:05.150
Sure I do.

42:05.510 --> 42:07.180
Back then, when it was my grandpa's
seventh day after passing,

42:07.180 --> 42:09.240
our whole family kept vigil. This...

42:09.300 --> 42:10.300
What's wrong, Mu?

42:10.590 --> 42:11.200
Mu?

42:24.030 --> 42:26.290
Did Zhang Fan give you these blueprints?

42:30.320 --> 42:31.380
You know Zhang Fan?

42:31.630 --> 42:33.360
Of course. He's from my school.

42:33.800 --> 42:35.070
I'm not a nerd.

42:35.260 --> 42:37.410
I know a lot more than you think, okay?

42:39.950 --> 42:40.760
Concerned?

42:42.940 --> 42:44.310
Who's concerned?

42:48.360 --> 42:49.760
I have to leave tomorrow.

42:50.550 --> 42:51.950
What's so urgent?

42:52.140 --> 42:52.930
It's about the car.
